   CLINTON-STARR-RDP (Washington) _ Lede-all; developments. By
Richard L. Berke.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-WHITEHOUSE (Washington) _ What all the documents say
about life inside the White House. By John M. Broder.
</P>
