faces the league's leading receiver in Lions' Herman Moore. ...
Moore has an NFL-best 22 catches for first downs. ... RB Curtis
Enis, with a team-high 262 yards, could get his first start for the
Bears. ... Detroit's Barry Sanders, who needs two rushing TDs for
100, had 328 rushing yards in two games against Chicago last
season. ... The Lions have won five of last six games in this
series.
</P>
<P>
   Favorite: Chicago by 1.
</P>
